item.title: By: Denys
item.dc:creator: Denys
item.description: I like the Origins products I use (the anti-aging eye cream and the anti-aging face cream). I read a review of the eye cream where a woman said she thought her eyes were being burnt from her skull. I thought she was a pussy. Not that you're a pussy. The eye cream helped relieve the dry, eczema patches I would get on my lids after using shitty eye shadow. Now I just use high end shadows, per your recommendation. Love you!
